text: US President Barack Obama ajusts his earphone during a news conference at the Merdeka Palace in Jakarta on November 9, 2010. Obama said it was 'wonderful' but also 'a little disorientating' to be back in Indonesia, where he spent four years as a schoolboy almost four decades ago.
